{"tid":478212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想同琴日係黃大仙執到銀包既你講聲多謝","createTime":"2017-11-24T00:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T02:18:56.000Z","uid":46610,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"00679117f4886c9f739877908a4be460460258e7","tid":478212,"uid":46610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:34:16.000Z","msg":"呢排心情非常唔好 生活不如意<br />\n如果琴日銀包成個冇左我真係會崩潰<br />\n所以唔知你睇唔睇到<br />\n坐係我隔離既絲打都好多謝你比粒定心丸我<br />\n執個個絲打雖然我唔知你係點樣<br />\n總之就好感激你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外各位巴絲打可唔可同你地乞句加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做人真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea2cdb537ee0eff7f5960bedf8f8b38920fd9af","tid":478212,"uid":57835,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:41:28.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f03857cd6b6199202594a753d13ca8a57d6703c","tid":478212,"uid":1565,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:44:01.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b991343af30fcb55375893a7fce5777291d43c5e","tid":478212,"uid":70205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:00:29.000Z","msg":"唔駛客氣"},{"pid":"ad2357175f37e411561be488c92d5b9a121573f5","tid":478212,"uid":61479,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:01:27.000Z","msg":"On9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ce86156466247c9e21f47957f9ce4fdeb809a2","tid":478212,"uid":150857,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"慳返淡氣暖肚啦"},{"pid":"b6942cdb522447472a11255e462c75af81242506","tid":478212,"uid":144843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit